    XDrawRectangle, XDrawRectangles, XRectangle - draw rectangles and
    rectangles structure

  SSYYNNTTAAXX

    XDrawRectangle(display, d, gc, x, y, width, height)
          Display *display;
          Drawable d;
          GC gc;
